text:
Lots of ?'s about #myocarditis 

Short answer - risk of myocarditis after COVID INFECTION is HIGHER than risk after #CovidVaccine 

Risk of myocarditis is generally LOW in 5-11 yo age group but we DON'T YET KNOW rate of myocarditis after vaccine in THIS age group.
